    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/530ee6ada388893d1f933b926a8e5865.poster.avif?t=1765987495\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/530ee6ada388893d1f933b926a8e5865.webm?t=1765987495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/530ee6ada388893d1f933b926a8e5865.mp4?t=1765987495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随条条光带，释放音乐中蕴藏的能量——在Aaero2中，闪速穿越令人感官震撼的外星世界。玩家可以独自飞行，也可以与好友组队游戏。对抗奇异的敌人和巨大的首领生物。一边听着由 Monstercat 创作的史诗级乐曲，一边降下由导弹弹幕和重型炮火组成的枪林弹雨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/e7366b69da067a5030485612fe89bd98.poster.avif?t=1765987495\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/e7366b69da067a5030485612fe89bd98.webm?t=1765987495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/e7366b69da067a5030485612fe89bd98.mp4?t=1765987495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由 Monstercat 授权提供的美妙音轨。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双人合作及 PvP 模式（单机或联机均可）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人惊叹的视觉和光影效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据每首音乐精心定制的游戏与环境体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全重新设计的全新战斗系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗巨大生物的史诗级首领战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aaero2 是 2017 年备受好评的音乐游戏 Aaero 的全新续作。我们细心考虑了对原作的每一条评论与反馈，并针对性地进行了优化和处理，才诞生了这款完全重新打造的全新游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/e5696cf368ae6fb2be69334501b76355.poster.avif?t=1765987495\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/e5696cf368ae6fb2be69334501b76355.webm?t=1765987495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010090/extras/e5696cf368ae6fb2be69334501b76355.mp4?t=1765987495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
